# CFF Personnel Planning API - Environment Configuration
# =============================================================================
# This API uses a split database architecture:
# - Internal DB: Local PostgreSQL container for parameters (constraints, weights)
# - External DB: Remote PostgreSQL server for production data
# =============================================================================

# =============================================================================
# Internal Database Configuration (Local Container - Parameters)
# Tables: legal_constraints, company_policy_constraints, objective_weights,
#         utilization_targets, audit_log
# =============================================================================
